{% block page_content %}
      <article class="pholder hpad post">
      	<h3 class="heading cf-secondary">wholesale opportunities</h3>
				<p>We are currently looking to partner with engaging and dynamic stores who wish to carry the Squatch.  We have had tremendous success with all types of stores including: groceries, gift shops, men's clothing or general stores, boutiques, and various online retail shops.</p>

				<p>For qualified retailers, we can offer competitive margins, dependable and speedy shipping times, and a unique, quality, handcrafted men's product.</p>

				<p>If you think your store would be a good fit, we would be thrilled to hear from you. Please include some details about your store in the form below and we will be happy to talk with you further about partnering.</p>	

				<h3 class="heading cf-secondary">current partners</h3>
				<img src="{{ 'images/brands.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" class="img-responsive">

				<h3 class="heading cf-secondary">get wholesale info</h3>
				<br>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-6">
    					{{ contact.contact_form("Wholesale Form") }}
					</div>
				</div>
      </article>
{% endblock %}

{% block page_javascript %}

<script src="js/jquery.formstyler.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
  (function() {
    setTimeout(function() {
      $('.cstyle').styler();
    }, 100);
  })();        
</script>

{% endblock %}
